== 國家隊生涯 ==
[[File:Kobe_Bryant_Beijing_Olympics_20080810_d-1024-627v.jpg|thumb]]，柯比避免與[[中国国家男子篮球队|中国国家男子篮球队]]球員發生碰撞]]
柯比因為休賽季要舉辦婚禮，婉拒參加{{tsl|en|2000 United States men's Olympic basketball team||2000年奧運}}<ref>{{cite news |author1=Mike Wise |title=Bryant Sets His Priorities |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/06/19/sports/nba-finals-lakers-vs-pacers-notebook-bryant-sets-his-priorities.html |work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |date=2000-06-19 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126224950/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/06/19/sports/nba-finals-lakers-vs-pacers-notebook-bryant-sets-his-priorities.html |archive-date=2020-01-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他同樣婉拒參加[[2002年世界篮球锦标赛|2002年世界篮球锦标赛]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=AP |title=U.S. ends losing streak at World Championship |url=https://archive.seattletimes.com/archive/?date=20020907&slug=hoop07 |work=[[西雅图时报|西雅图时报]] |date=2002-09-07 |accessdate=2020-01-31 |archive-date=2021-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612235552/https://archive.seattletimes.com/archive/?date=20020907&slug=hoop07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2003年，科比最初有入選FIBA美洲冠軍賽球員名單，但在肩膀接受關節鏡檢查和膝關節手術後退出<ref>{{cite news |title=Vince Carter Added to Olympic Qualifying Team |url=http://www.insidehoops.com/carter-olympic-072903.shtml |work=InsideHoops NBA |date=2003-07-29 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126224952/http://www.insidehoops.com/carter-olympic-072903.shtml |archive-date=2020-01-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。隔年夏天由於[[#性侵案|性侵案]]發生，他不得不退出奧運隊<ref>{{cite web |title=Olympic Basketball |url=http://www.insidehoops.com/olympics.shtml |website=InsideHoops NBA |date=2008 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226033223/http://www.insidehoops.com/olympics.shtml |archive-date=2019-12-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2006-2008年美國初選球員名單，科比與[[勒布朗·詹姆斯|勒布朗·詹姆斯]]為入選的首批兩名球員<ref>{{cite news |title=Kobe will play for U.S. at worlds, '08 Olympics |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/oly/news/story?id=2300053 |work=ESPN |date=2006-01-21 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105102000/http://sports.espn.go.com/oly/news/story?id=2300053 |archive-date=2016-01-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是因膝蓋手術無法參加[[2006年世界籃球錦標賽|2006年世界籃球錦標賽]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Kobe won't play for USA after knee surgery |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2520373 |work=ESPN |date=2006-07-16 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831131344/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2520373 |archive-date=2006-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科比的[[美国国家篮球队|美國國家隊]]生涯最終從2007年開始。他是2007年美國男子高級國家隊和美國FIBA美洲冠軍隊的成員，國家隊以10勝0負奪得冠軍，並獲得2008年奧運的美國男子籃球參賽資格。在美國FIBA美洲錦標賽的所有10場比賽，科比皆為先發。科比場均成績為15.3分，2.9次助攻，2.0個籃板和1.6次抄截<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usabasketball.com/men_team.php?bios=bryant_kobe |title=USA Basketball |publisher=USABasketball.com |accessdate=2008-06-18 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080702194340/http://www.usabasketball.com/men_team.php?bios=bryant_kobe |archivedate=2008-07-02 }}</ref>。

2008年6月23日，他入選{{tsl|en|2008 United States men's Olympic basketball team||2008年夏季奧運}}[[美国国家篮球队|美國國家隊]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=oly&id=3457017 |title=James, Bryant to lead US team |publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]].com |accessdate=2008-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629035536/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=oly&id=3457017 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這是他第一次參加奧運。隨著美國隊在2008年8月24日的[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會男子籃球賽|金牌戰]]中以118-107擊敗西班牙，這是自{{tsl|en|2000 United States men's Olympic basketball team||2000年奧運}}以來在重大賽事的首枚金牌，科比該場賽事獲得20分，包括第四節的13分和6次助攻<ref>{{cite web |last=Mahoney |first=Brian |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2008-08-24-1012609106_x.htm |title=US hoops back on top, beats Spain for gold medal |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |date=2008-08-24 |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091418/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2008-08-24-1012609106_x.htm |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会美国男子篮球队|2012年夏季奧運]]，科比重返[[美国国家篮球队|美國國家隊]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Kobe commits to Team USA |url=http://www.foxsportswest.com/11/02/10/Kobe-commits-to-Team-USA/landing_lakers.html?blockID=344392&feedID=3657 |agency=Associated Press |publisher=Fox News |date=2010-11-02 |accessdate=2010-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724083736/http://www.foxsportswest.com/11/02/10/Kobe-commits-to-Team-USA/landing_lakers.html?blockID=344392&feedID=3657 |archive-date=2013-07-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在贏得另一枚金牌後，科比決定從國家隊退役<ref>{{cite news | url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/sports/2012/08/13/lebron-helps-us-beat-spain-in-tight-olympic-final/ | work=Fox News | title=USA Basketball Wins Gold Over Spain, Rio Next in 2016 | date=2012-08-13 | access-date=2020-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305001243/http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/sports/2012/08/13/lebron-helps-us-beat-spain-in-tight-olympic-final/ | archive-date=2016-03-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。科比共參加三個賽事，以26勝0負戰績和每次賽事均獲得金牌後結束國家隊生涯<ref>{{cite news|last=Whitfield|first=Nick|title=Kobe Bryant and USA Basketball – Whatever It Takes|url=https://www.sportingnews.com/us/fiba/news/kobe-bryant-and-usa-basketball-whatever-it-takes/1woyvmlziow1p1i9xcyyxq7yhl|work=Sporting News|date=2018-10-31|accessdate=2020-02-06|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207073915/https://www.sportingnews.com/us/fiba/news/kobe-bryant-and-usa-basketball-whatever-it-takes/1woyvmlziow1p1i9xcyyxq7yhl|archive-date=2020-02-07}}</ref>。

== 球員資料 ==
[[File:Kobe_Bryant_Shane_Battier.jpg|thumb]]防守下[[后仰投篮|后仰投篮]]]]
柯比場上主要打的位置是[[得分后卫|得分后卫]]。他的身高為{{convert|6|ft|6|in|m}}、體重為{{convert|212|lb|kg}}<ref name=Reference>{{cite web|title=Kobe Bryant NBA|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/b/bryanko01.html|publisher=Basketball Reference|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67VEeNbPP?url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/b/bryanko01.html|archive-date=2012-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，雖然柯比說過他自己身高是{{convert|6|ft|4|in|m}}或穿著鞋子「可能」只有{{convert|6|ft|5|in|m}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Mallozzi |first=Vincent |title='Where's Kobe? I Want Kobe.' |date=2006-12-24 |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/12/24/sports/basketball/24cheer.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6EbfVb425?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/12/24/sports/basketball/24cheer.html?_r=1& |archivedate=2013-02-21 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Ding |first=Kevin |title=Kobe Bryant's work with kids brings joy, though sometimes it's fleeting |date=2008-01-08 |newspaper=Orange County Register |url=http://www.ocregister.com/sports/kobebryant-88229-makeawishfoundation-lakers.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ebfn5UQs?url=http://www.ocregister.com/sports/kobebryant-88229-makeawishfoundation-lakers.html |archivedate=2013-02-21 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。他經常被舉例為NBA中最危險的射手之一<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/2006-01-23-100-points_x.htm | work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] | title=Anyone up for 100? | first1=David | last1=DuPree | date=2006-01-24 | accessdate=2010-05-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524084301/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/2006-01-23-100-points_x.htm | archive-date=2010-05-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Pelton|first=Kevin|title=Los Angeles Lakers: 2013–14 roster (Subscription Required)|url=http://insider.espn.go.com/nba/preview2013/story/_/page/2013-14-lal-preview/los-angeles-lakers-player-profiles|publisher=ESPN Insider|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015104444/http://insider.espn.go.com/nba/preview2013/story/_/page/2013-14-lal-preview/los-angeles-lakers-player-profiles|archive-date=2013-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柯比常常被拿來和喬丹相比，而柯比的籃球動作就是參仿自喬丹<ref>{{cite web|title=Michael Jordan eases off talk|url=http://espn.go.com/chicago/nba/story/_/id/9764802/michael-jordan-says-kobe-bryant-lebron-james|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014005006/http://espn.go.com/chicago/nba/story/_/id/9764802/michael-jordan-says-kobe-bryant-lebron-james|archive-date=2013-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1={{tsl|en|Marc Stein (reporter)||Marc Stein}} |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=1270487&type=columnist |title=Kobe, Hill deal with being the next Michael |work={{tsl|en|ESPN.com||ESPN.com}} |date=2001-10-29 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806032108/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=1270487&type=columnist |archive-date=2009-08-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=hoffman_12132014>{{cite news|last=Hoffman|first=Benjamin|title=Kobe Bryant Is Nearly an Equal of Michael Jordan, Except in Fan Adoration|date=2014-12-13|newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/14/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-is-nearly-an-equal-of-michael-jordan-except-in-fan-adoration.html|accessdate=2014-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324150619/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/14/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-is-nearly-an-equal-of-michael-jordan-except-in-fan-adoration.html|archive-date=2015-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，比如最知名就是喬丹的[[后仰投篮|后仰投篮]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Holmes|first=Baxter|title=Kobe Bryant rises up before falling away|date=2014-12-14|publisher=ESPN|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40621/kobe-bryant-rises-up-before-falling-away|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215122603/http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40621/kobe-bryant-rises-up-before-falling-away|archivedate=2014-12-15|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-02-01}}</ref>。《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》的克里斯·巴拉德（Chris Ballard）描述柯比另一個知名的籃球動作是「刺探並急停」（jab step-and-pause）：柯比使用非[[走步|軸心腳]]向前刺探促使防守者鬆懈，但會突然收回非軸心腳而拉開與防守者的距離以能順利得分<ref>{{cite news |author1=Chris Ballard |title=Kobe's Killer Instinct (cont.) |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2008/writers/chris_ballard/05/27/kobe0602/1.html |accessdate=2010-11-20 |work=[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]] |date=2010-02-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100217183232/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2008/writers/chris_ballard/05/27/kobe0602/1.html |archivedate=2010-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

柯比因能在比分接近的關鍵時刻順利投籃進球而為自身建立聲望<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Baxter |title=Kobe Bryant delivers the final miss again |date=2014-12-20 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40674/kobe-bryant-delivers-the-final-miss-again |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V01uNybx?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40674/kobe-bryant-delivers-the-final-miss-again |archivedate=2014-12-22 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Harper |first=Zach |title=Lakers' Jeremy Lin on game winners: 'I would love to shoot some' |date=2014-12-20 |work=CBSSports.com |url=http://www.cbssports.com/nba/eye-on-basketball/24904469/lakers-jeremy-lin-on-game-winners-i-would-love-to-shoot-some |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V02REEVh?url=http://www.cbssports.com/nba/eye-on-basketball/24904469/lakers-jeremy-lin-on-game-winners-i-would-love-to-shoot-some |archivedate=2014-12-22 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Jenkins |first=Bruce |title=Jenkins on NBA: Bryant becomes more gunner than top gun |date=2014-12-20 |work=SFGate.com |url=http://www.sfgate.com/sports/jenkins/article/Jenkins-on-NBA-Bryant-becomes-more-gunner-than-5971200.php |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V02omWa4?url=http://www.sfgate.com/sports/jenkins/article/Jenkins-on-NBA-Bryant-becomes-more-gunner-than-5971200.php |archivedate=2014-12-22 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，儘管他被[[包夾|包夾]]或是三夾<ref name=pingue_11302015/>，並被公認為是聯盟最出色的絕殺球員（premier closers）之一<ref name=pingue_11302015/><ref>{{cite news |author1=McMenamin, Dave |title=Shots heard 'round the world |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/columns/story?id=4983889 |accessdate=2010-11-14 |work=ESPN |date=2010-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629035523/http://sports.espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/columns/story?id=4983889 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一份在2012年對NBA球隊總經理的年度調查中，科比連續10個賽季被選為總經理希望關鍵時刻出手的球員<ref>{{cite news |title=2011–12 NBA.com GM Survey Results |date=2012-01-17 |work=NBA.com |url=http://www.nba.com/news/features/2012-gm-survey/index.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67UdhkP2F?url=http://www.nba.com/news/features/2012-gm-survey/index.html |archivedate=2012-05-07 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref name=“Crunch”/>。柯比樂於當籃球場上的惡棍，並且陶醉於球迷因他的表現而發出的噓聲或沉靜<ref name=smallwood_02062012>{{cite news |last=Smallwood |first=John |title=Love him or not, Kobe Bryant a Philly player |date=2012-02-06 |website=Philly.com |url=http://articles.philly.com/2012-02-06/sports/31030484_1_philadelphia-and-bryant-nba-mvp-gregg-downer |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dRs8t3cd?url=http://articles.philly.com/2012-02-06/sports/31030484_1_philadelphia-and-bryant-nba-mvp-gregg-downer |archivedate=2015-12-01 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref name=brewer_12022015>{{cite news |last=Brewer |first=Jerry |title=During strange farewell tour, Kobe Bryant rediscovers greatness for one night in D.C. |date=2015-12-02 |newspaper=The Washington Post |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/wizards/kobe-bryants-complicated-farewell-tour-makes-latest-awkward-stop-in-washington/2015/12/02/264b8e3e-9941-11e5-94f0-9eeaff906ef3_story.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6f2fDWtgU?url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/wizards/kobe-bryants-complicated-farewell-tour-makes-latest-awkward-stop-in-washington/2015/12/02/264b8e3e-9941-11e5-94f0-9eeaff906ef3_story.html |archivedate=2016-02-04 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=Amid the Points and Applause, One Single Shot Ignited Love Story of Kobe, NYC |date=2015-11-09 |work=Bleacher Report |url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2587406-amid-the-points-and-applause-one-single-shot-ignited-love-story-of-kobe-nyc |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dRw1AAX1?url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2587406-amid-the-points-and-applause-one-single-shot-ignited-love-story-of-kobe-nyc |archivedate=2015-12-01 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。他的高難度進球能力也引起對他出手選擇的批評<ref name=hoffman_12132014/><ref name=espn_sg_rank_2016/>。他的整個職業生涯，科比因個性自私、是一名需大量出手的射手而被貶損<ref name=“Crunch”>{{cite web |last=Abbot |first=Henry |title=The truth about Kobe Bryant in crunch time |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/24200/the-truth-about-kobe-bryant-in-crunch-time |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2013-10-12 |date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127005105/http://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/24200/the-truth-about-kobe-bryant-in-crunch-time |archive-date=2017-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=lowe_top100>{{cite web |last=Lowe |first=Zach |title=Top 100 NBA Players — Nos. 1–10 |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/basketball/nba/blogs/nba-point-forward/2011/08/16/top-100-nba-players-nos-1-10/ |work=Sports Illustrated |accessdate=2013-10-12 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005010519/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/basketball/nba/blogs/nba-point-forward/2011/08/16/top-100-nba-players-nos-1-10/ |archivedate=2013-10-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Moore |first=Tom |title=Kobe Bryant set to play final game in Philadelphia |date=2015-11-30 |newspaper=The Morning Call |url=http://www.mcall.com/sports/basketball/sixers/mc-kobe-final-game-in-philly-1130-20151130-story.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dRtqZ3q1?url=http://www.mcall.com/sports/basketball/sixers/mc-kobe-final-game-in-philly-1130-20151130-story.html |archivedate=2015-12-01 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>；柯比職業生涯中投籃沒進總數超過聯盟歷史上任何其他球員{{notetag|2014年，科比投籃沒進總數超越[[约翰·哈夫利切克|约翰·哈夫利切克]]的13,417次<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Baxter |title=Misses add up to big part of Kobe's legacy |date=2014-11-11 |work=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40363/misses-add-up-to-big-part-of-kobes-legacy |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6U2UFPSIh?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40363/misses-add-up-to-big-part-of-kobes-legacy |archivedate=2014-11-12 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，退休時總數累計至14,481次。}}。曾執教科比多年的[[菲尔·杰克逊|菲尔·杰克逊]]表示，科比「傾向於強迫行為（force the action），尤其在比賽進展不佳的時候。當他的投籃不順暢時，科比會埋頭苦幹直到運氣好轉為止」<ref>{{cite news|last=Bresnahan|first=Mike|title=Phil Jackson throws the book at Kobe Bryant|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/16/sports/la-sp-phil-jackson-kobe-20130516|newspaper=The Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022131139/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/16/sports/la-sp-phil-jackson-kobe-20130516|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據柯比自身說法：「我寧願30投0中，而不要9投0中；9投0中意味著你擊敗了自己，讓自己在比賽中迷失自我」<ref name=hoffman_11302015>{{cite news |last=Hoffman |first=Benjamin |title=In Most Areas, Good or Bad, Kobe Bryant Has Simply Done More |date=2015-11-30 |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/01/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-retire.html?_r=0 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dXCZD5OS?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/01/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-retire.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2015-12-04 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。

除了他在進攻端的能力外，科比還確立自己作為出色防守球員的地位<ref>{{cite news |last=Pelton |first=Kevin |title=Every Play Counts: Kobe Bryant |date=2005-11-07 |work=82games.com |url=http://www.82games.com/pelton8.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V1ulG89Z?url=http://www.82games.com/pelton8.htm |archivedate=2014-12-23 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。科比很少在防守時[[侵人犯規|侵人犯規]]，他認為這可以保護他的身體並延展他的籃球生涯<ref>{{cite news |last=McMenamin |first=Dave |title=Kobe Bryant: Charges carry big risk |date=2012-05-17 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/7935166/2012-nba-playoffs-los-angeles-lakers-kobe-bryant-cites-injury-risk-drawing-charges |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/694divRK2?url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/7935166/2012-nba-playoffs-los-angeles-lakers-kobe-bryant-cites-injury-risk-drawing-charges |archivedate=2012-07-11 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。一些評論家認為，科比籃球生涯晚年的防守表現大多是基於他的聲譽而不是他的實際表現<ref name=medina_05092011>{{cite news |last=Medina |first=Mark |title=Kobe Bryant named to NBA's all-defensive first team for ninth time |date=2011-05-09 |newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |url=http://lakersblog.latimes.com/lakersblog/2011/05/kobe-bryant-named-to-nbas-all-defensive-team-for-ninth-time.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V1v8AawK?url=http://lakersblog.latimes.com/lakersblog/2011/05/kobe-bryant-named-to-nbas-all-defensive-team-for-ninth-time.html |archivedate=2014-12-23 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref name=lowe_05262013>{{cite news |last=Lowe |first=Zach |title=An Open Letter to Kobe Bryant About His Defense |date=2013-05-26 |work=Grantland |url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/an-open-letter-to-kobe-bryant-about-his-defense/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V1vGji3k?url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/an-open-letter-to-kobe-bryant-about-his-defense/ |archivedate=2014-12-23 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Paine |first=Neal |title=Once And For All: Michael Jordan Was Way Better Than Kobe Bryant |date=2014-12-12 |work=FiveThirtyEight |url=http://fivethirtyeight.com/datalab/michael-jordan-kobe-bryant/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6V1vTNNJJ?url=http://fivethirtyeight.com/datalab/michael-jordan-kobe-bryant/ |archivedate=2014-12-23 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。

科比還因其運動道德受到稱讚<ref>{{cite news |last=Shelburne |first=Ramona |title=Kobe and L.A. tradition will be tested |date=2013-04-13 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9167365/los-angeles-lakers-guard-kobe-bryant-achilles-injury-signal-end-lakers-era |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Fqyo6U8A?url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9167365/los-angeles-lakers-guard-kobe-bryant-achilles-injury-signal-end-lakers-era |archivedate=2013-04-13 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。在他生涯前16個賽季中，他的身體富有彈性<ref name=ap_01262015>{{cite news |title=Kobe Bryant to have shoulder surgery |date=2015-01-26 |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/12232146/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-shoulder-surgery |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VsrcrK5o?url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/12232146/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-shoulder-surgery |archivedate=2015-01-27 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，並且經常在因傷病中打球而展現出很高的{{tsl|en|pain threshold||疼痛閾值}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Adande |first=J. A. |title=Kobe Bryant pays price for greatness |date=2015-01-26 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/12222849/kobe-bryant-pays-price-greatness-requires |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VszidAJN?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/12222849/kobe-bryant-pays-price-greatness-requires |archivedate=2015-01-27 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Ballard |first=Chris |title=Examining Kobe Bryant's legendary pain tolerance and road to recovery |date=2014-08-26 |work=Sports Illustrated |url=https://www.si.com/edge/2014/08/28/kobe-bryant-recovery-lakers-judy-seto-knee-injury |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Vt0HJz2C?url=http://www.si.com/edge/2014/08/28/kobe-bryant-recovery-lakers-judy-seto-knee-injury |archivedate=2015-01-27 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。柯比是一位狂熱的球員，他會把對手和隊友成為他的輕蔑對象<ref>{{cite news |last=Phillips |first=Brian |title=Wolf on the Rock: The Ludicrous, Glorious Doom of Kobe Bryant |date=2015-01-08 |work=Grantland |url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/wolf-on-the-rock-the-ludicrous-glorious-doom-of-kobe-bryant/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fFiWq5Kh?url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/wolf-on-the-rock-the-ludicrous-glorious-doom-of-kobe-bryant/ |archivedate=2016-02-12 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Ryan |first1=Chris |last2=Concepcion |first2=Jason |title=Six Seconds to Perfection: The Best NBA Vines of the Season |date=2015-02-17 |work=Grantland |url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/six-seconds-to-perfection-the-best-nba-vines-of-the-season/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fFigOhsX?url=http://grantland.com/the-triangle/six-seconds-to-perfection-the-best-nba-vines-of-the-season/ |archivedate=2016-02-12 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，且他在場上的投入和表現水平很高，因此許多球員認為很難與他打球<ref name=ding_102202014>{{cite news |last=Ding |first=Kevin |title=Julius Randle's Development Poses Final Leadership Test for Kobe Bryant |date=2014-10-22 |work=BleacherReport.com |url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2240663-julius-randles-development-poses-final-leadership-test-for-kobe-bryant |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TYMaO8Dc?url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2240663-julius-randles-development-poses-final-leadership-test-for-kobe-bryant |archivedate=2014-10-24 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Markazi |first=Arash |title=Long a tough, chilly teammate, Kobe Bryant has mellowed and now is a mentor |date=2014-10-12 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40163/long-a-tough-chilly-teammate-kobe-bryant-has-mellowed-and-now-is-a-mentor |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TYMl1a0W?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/40163/long-a-tough-chilly-teammate-kobe-bryant-has-mellowed-and-now-is-a-mentor |archivedate=2014-10-24 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Abbott |first=Henry |title=Kobe |date=2014-10-20 |magazine=ESPN The Magazine |url=http://espn.go.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/11717596/is-kobe-bryant-reason-los-angeles-lakers-downfall |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TYMukOau?url=http://espn.go.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/11717596/is-kobe-bryant-reason-los-angeles-lakers-downfall |archivedate=2014-10-24 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。
根據《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》體育記者馬克·海斯勒（Mark Heisler）表示，「大約在2004-2007年間，科比是我見過最不受歡迎（the most alienated）的NBA超級巨星」<ref name=heisler_10222014>{{cite news |last=Heisler |first=Mark |title=Who Killed Lakers? ESPN Says It Was Someone on Inside With the Initials Kobe Bryant |date=2014-10-22 |work=Forbes.com |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/markheisler/2014/10/22/who-killed-lakers-espn-says-it-was-someone-on-inside-with-the-initials-kobe-bryant/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6TYNKpw6b?url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/markheisler/2014/10/22/who-killed-lakers-espn-says-it-was-someone-on-inside-with-the-initials-kobe-bryant/ |archivedate=2014-10-24 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。然而在[[沙奎尔·奥尼尔|沙奎尔·奥尼尔]]離開湖人後，他帶領湖人獲得兩座冠軍；在此期間，他比以前更像是隊友的良師益友<ref name=ding_102202014/><ref name=heisler_10222014/>。科比過往的總教練[[菲尔·杰克逊|菲尔·杰克逊]]指出，科比在他執教湖人的第一時期和第二時期最大的區別是，早期的科比通常會向隊友喊「給我該死的球」，而後期的柯比「會擁抱球隊和他的隊友，並在旅途中打電話給他們，邀請他們出門吃飯。好像其他球員現在是他的伙伴，而不是他個人的不重要配角（{{tsl|en|Spear carrier||Spear-carrier}}）」<ref>{{cite news|last=Bresnahan|first=Mike|title=Phil Jackson's new book focuses a lot on (who else?) Kobe Bryant|date=2013-05-16|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/16/sports/la-sp-ln-phil-jackson-new-book-kobe-bryant-20130515|access-date=2020-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419212759/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/16/sports/la-sp-ln-phil-jackson-new-book-kobe-bryant-20130515|archive-date=2016-04-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 球衣號碼 ==
科比過去曾經穿著「8」號和「24」號球衣，科比1996年加入湖人之後，他選擇8號的原因是高中時所穿的33號球衣在湖人已退休，由於科比曾經在Adidas的ABCD訓練營穿過143號背號，就將三個數字加起來，成為了8號球衣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2421874|title=Bryant will hang up his No. 8 jersey, sources say|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2006-04-26|accessdate=2016-04-24|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425162440/http://espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2421874|archive-date=2016-04-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直至2006年改穿24號球衣，科比當時對此事不願多談<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macauslot.com/slot/html/news/news_2_2_060428_85134.html|title=高比拜仁拒談換號碼事件|publisher=[[澳門彩票|澳門彩票]]|date=2006-04-28|accessdate=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929054010/http://www.macauslot.com/slot/html/news/news_2_2_060428_85134.html|archive-date=2016-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到2013年科比才公開表示換號的原因，說「選擇24號是為了提醒自己，一天有24小時，每一分鐘都必須努力，不能鬆懈」<ref>{{cite news |author1=氙的世界 |title=24個關鍵詞致敬科比系列之——8-24 |url=http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/news/spt/nba/sinacn/20160331/08597257782.html |accessdate=2020-01-31 |work=北京新浪網 |date=2016-03-31 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801165306/http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/news/spt/nba/sinacn/20160331/08597257782.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=蕭玉品 |title=用24號警惕自己絕不鬆懈！NBA一代球星科比的傳奇故事 |url=https://www.gvm.com.tw/article/70701 |accessdate=2020-01-31 |work=遠見雜誌 |date=2020-01-27 |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420220236/https://www.gvm.com.tw/article/70701 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

* 8：1996年至2006年湖人的背號。
* 10：[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]、[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]，國家隊的背號。
* 24：高中時候曾穿過，2006年至2016年湖人的背號。
* 33：奪得高中聯賽冠軍那年的背號，父親曾穿過的背號。

== 生涯成就 ==
