[[File:Kobe_Bryant_2014.jpg|thumb]]
NBA主席[[蕭華_(NBA)|蕭華]]在柯比退休時表示「柯比是聯盟史上最偉大球員之一」<ref name=keh_11292015>{{cite news |last=Keh |first=Andrew |title=Kobe Bryant Announces Retirement |date=2015-11-29 |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/30/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-announces-retirement.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dQ5jS7dr?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/30/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-announces-retirement.html?hp |archivedate=2015-11-30 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-09-10 }}</ref>，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》寫道「他擁有運動史上最華麗的籃球生涯」<ref name=keh_11292015/>，《[[路透社|路透社]]》稱他「可能是他同屆球員中最佳球員」<ref name=pingue_11302015>{{cite news |last=Pingue |first=Frank |title=Kobe Bryant to retire at end of season |date=2015-11-30 |agency=Reuters |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/30/us-nba-bryant-idUSKBN0TJ00B20151130#bK9r5HY9zI03wKtQ.97 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dQQXqXa9?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/30/us-nba-bryant-idUSKBN0TJ00B20151130#bK9r5HY9zI03wKtQ.97 |archivedate=2015-11-30 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，而{{tsl|en|Sporting News||Sporting News}}和[[特纳电视网|特纳电视网]]都評他為聯盟2000年代代表球員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/sports/kobe-bryant-elected-as-the-nba-player-of-the-decade_100320608.html |title=Kobe Bryant Elected As The NBA Player Of The Decade |publisher=Thaindian.com |date=2010-02-15 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609142228/http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/sports/kobe-bryant-elected-as-the-nba-player-of-the-decade_100320608.html |archive-date=2010-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/nba/article/2009-09-24/sporting-news-nba-athlete-decade-kobe-bryant-sg-lakers |title=Sporting News' NBA Athlete of the Decade: Kobe Bryant, SG, Lakers |magazine=Sporting News |accessdate=2010-06-08 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412122936/http://www.sportingnews.com/nba/article/2009-09-24/sporting-news-nba-athlete-decade-kobe-bryant-sg-lakers |archivedate=2010-04-12 }}</ref>。2008年和2016年，ESPN排名柯比為史上第二偉大[[得分后卫|得分后卫]]，僅次於喬丹<ref name=espn_sg_rank_2016>{{cite news |title=All-Time #NBArank: Michael Jordan tops list of best shooting guards |date=2016-01-19 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/page/nbarankSGs/ranking-top-10-shooting-guards-ever |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fFk5zYXs?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/page/nbarankSGs/ranking-top-10-shooting-guards-ever |archivedate=2016-02-12 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref name="ESPN">{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/dailydime?page=dime-GreatestSGs |title=Special Dime: Greatest shooting guards of all time |publisher=ESPN |date=2008-03-11 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629035432/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/dailydime?page=dime-GreatestSGs |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球員包括[[凯文·杜兰特|凯文·杜兰特]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Young |first=Royce |title=Kevin Durant frustrated by media's handling of Kobe Bryant |date=2015-12-01 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14261276/kevin-durant-oklahoma-city-thunder-discusses-idolizing-treatment-retiring-kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6etSsOPGX?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14261276/kevin-durant-oklahoma-city-thunder-discusses-idolizing-treatment-retiring-kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers |archivedate=2016-01-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>、[[德克·诺维茨基|德克·诺维茨基]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Baxter |title=Kobe will miss talking trash with Dirk Nowitzki |date=2016-01-27 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/42641/kobe-bryant-recalls-18-seasons-of-facing-dirk-nowitzki |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6etTKWTyg?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/42641/kobe-bryant-recalls-18-seasons-of-facing-dirk-nowitzki |archivedate=2016-01-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>、[[德维恩·韦德|德维恩·韦德]]<ref name=jackson_02022016>{{cite news |last=Jackson |first=Scoop |title=Dwyane Wade: 'I never thought I'd be Top 100 all time' |date=2016-02-02 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14695748/dwyane-wade-place-nba-history |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6f2f6GWk9?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14695748/dwyane-wade-place-nba-history |archivedate=2016-02-04 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>和[[德里克·罗斯|德里克·罗斯]]稱，都將柯比視為他們世代的「喬丹」<ref>{{cite news |last=Friedell |first=Nick |title=Rose: Kobe is the Jordan of our generation |date=2016-01-28 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/chicago/bulls/post/_/id/22848/rose-kobe-is-the-jordan-of-our-generation |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6etTV81al?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/chicago/bulls/post/_/id/22848/rose-kobe-is-the-jordan-of-our-generation |archivedate=2016-01-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hoffman |first=Benjamin |title=To the End, Kobe Bryant Is a Shooting Guard, Hot or Cold |date=2014-11-15 |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/16/sports/basketball/to-the-end-kobe-bryant-is-a-shooting-guard-hot-or-cold.html?_r=0 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6etRw8sWR?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/16/sports/basketball/to-the-end-kobe-bryant-is-a-shooting-guard-hot-or-cold.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2016-01-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|The Press-Enterprise||The Press-Enterprise}}》描述他「也許是湖人史上最偉大球員」<ref>{{cite news |last=Woike |first=Dan |title=Kobe Bryant announces plans to retire following this season |date=2015-11-29 |newspaper=The Press-Enterprise |url=http://www.pe.com/articles/season-787798-bryant-retire.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dQNiRYol?url=http://www.pe.com/articles/season-787798-bryant-retire.html |archivedate=2015-11-30 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。柯比為湖人隊史得分王以及他握有五只冠軍戒追平隊史紀錄<ref name=espn_11292015>{{cite news |title=Top stats to know: Kobe Bryant's statistical legacy |date=2015-11-29 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/112016/top-stats-to-know-kobe-bryants-statistical-legacy |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dQA0Qf5K?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/112016/top-stats-to-know-kobe-bryants-statistical-legacy |archivedate=2015-11-30 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。2017年12月18日，湖人退休柯比籃球生涯穿過的8號及24號球衣<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/21811693/nba-kobe-bryant-gets-8-24-retired-close-warriors-lakers-matchup|title=Kobe Bryant has numbers 8 and 24 retired by the Lakers|last=Arnovitz|first=Kevin|work=ESPN|date=2017-12-19|accessdate=2017-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052600/http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/21811693/nba-kobe-bryant-gets-8-24-retired-close-warriors-lakers-matchup|archive-date=2017-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

柯比生涯場均成績為25分，5.2籃板，4.7助攻以及1.4抄截<ref name=Reference/>。他被視為聯盟史上最完美（the most complete）球員之一<ref name="hh">{{cite web |title=NBA Players – Kobe Bryant |url=http://hoopshype.com/players/kobe_bryant.htm |website=HoopsHype.com |accessdate=2007-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126005607/http://hoopshype.com/players/kobe_bryant.htm |archive-date=2010-11-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。柯比是聯盟第一位得分至少30,000分和送出6,000次助攻的球員<ref name=holmes_11302014>{{cite news|last1=Holmes|first1=Baxter|title=Kobe gets milestone on 6,000th assist|url=http://espn.go.com/losangeles/nba/story/_/id/11961944/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-becomes-first-player-nba-history-30000-points-6000-assists|accessdate=2014-12-01|publisher=ESPN|date=2014-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204023223/http://espn.go.com/losangeles/nba/story/_/id/11961944/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-becomes-first-player-nba-history-30000-points-6000-assists|archive-date=2014-12-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及四位球員之一得分至少25,000分、抓下6,000籃板和送出6,000次助攻<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Baxter |title=Kobe Bryant says he knew from onset that 2015–16 would be final season |date=2015-11-30 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14257274/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-says-knew-2015-16-final-season |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dXpvvSKC?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14257274/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-says-knew-2015-16-final-season |archivedate=2015-12-05 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。柯比在{{nbay|2005}}至{{nbay|2006}}賽季榮獲[[NBA历届得分王|聯盟得分王]]<ref name="bio" />。2006年，柯比對上暴龍時創下例行賽得分81分，為聯盟史上{{tsl|en|List of National Basketball Association single-game scoring leaders||單場得分}}第二高<ref name="tor">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/recap?gameId=260122013|title=Kobe's 81-point game second only to Wilt|date=2006-01-12|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|accessdate=2008-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524210519/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/recap?gameId=260122013|archive-date=2011-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，僅次於1962年{{tsl|en|Wilt Chamberlain's 100-point game||威爾特·張伯倫的100分}}。柯比生涯得分至少50分有24場，在聯盟史上排名第三，僅次於張伯倫的118場和喬丹的31場<ref name=lakers_11292015>{{cite web |title=LOS ANGELES LAKERS (2–13) VS. INDIANA PACERS (10–5) |date=2015-11-29 |work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |url=http://www.nba.com/gamenotes/lakers.pdf?ls=nav_news&cid=nav_news |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dPyOLrex?url=http://www.nba.com/gamenotes/lakers.pdf?ls=nav_news&cid=nav_news |archivedate=2015-11-30 |dead-url=no |access-date=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，柯比生涯有6次得分至少60分<ref name=martin_11292015>{{cite news |last=Martin |first=Brian |date=2015-11-29 |title=KOBE BY THE NUMBERS |website=NBA.com |url=http://stats.nba.com/featured/kobe_by_the_numbers_2015_11_29.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dRxcqrA6?url=http://stats.nba.com/featured/kobe_by_the_numbers_2015_11_29.html |archivedate=2015-12-01 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>；他是聯盟歷史上第三位單月平均得分超過40分的球員，并且生涯4次達成此成就{{notetag|張伯倫達成15次，[[艾爾金·貝勒|艾爾金·貝勒]]則為1次<ref name=espn_12142014>{{cite news|title=Bryant passes Jordan, has shot to be No. 1|date=2014-12-14|publisher=ESPN|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/100032/bryant-passes-jordan-has-shot-to-be-no-1|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215084246/http://espn.go.com/blog/statsinfo/post/_/id/100032/bryant-passes-jordan-has-shot-to-be-no-1|archivedate=2014-12-15|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-02-01}}</ref>。}}。2008年，柯比被票選為[[NBA最有价值球员|NBA最有价值球员]]，並率領球隊以西區第一種子晉級[[2008年NBA總決賽|2008年NBA總決賽]]<ref name="Kobe MVP">{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com//news/kobe_mvp_080506.html|title=Kobe Bryant Wins Most Valuable Player Award|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|date=2008-05-06|accessdate=2008-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901171948/http://www.nba.com/news/kobe_mvp_080506.html|archive-date=2010-09-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2008年夏季奧運]]，他以[[美國國家男子籃球隊|美國國家隊]]身分榮獲一枚[[金牌|金牌]]，經常被稱為「救贖隊」<ref name="RedeemTeambySheridan">{{cite web|last=Sheridan|first=Chris|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/oly/summer08/basketball/columns/story?columnist=sheridan_chris&page=DreamRedeem-080825|title=Redeem Team proves worthy of Dream Team comparison|publisher=ESPN|date=2008-08-25|accessdate=2008-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105102000/http://sports.espn.go.com/oly/summer08/basketball/columns/story?columnist=sheridan_chris&page=DreamRedeem-080825|archive-date=2016-01-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2012年夏季奧運]]，他榮獲另外一枚金牌。2009年和2010年，他率領湖人奪下兩座冠軍，並兩年都被票選為[[NBA总决赛最有价值球员|NBA总决赛最有价值球员]]。

柯比共入選明賽18次，僅次於[[卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔|卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔]]的19次<ref name=espn_01212016>{{cite news |title=Kobe Bryant top vote-getter for 18th and final All-Star Game |date=2016-01-21 |publisher=ESPN |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14622192/top-vote-getter-kobe-bryant-gets-start-final-all-star-game |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eicI3E8r?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/14622192/top-vote-getter-kobe-bryant-gets-start-final-all-star-game |archivedate=2016-01-22 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，他連續18年入選，每次都是以先發球員上場<ref name=bresnahan_01222015>{{cite news |last=Bresnahan |first=Mike |title=Lakers' Kobe Bryant has torn rotator cuff; severity to be determined |date=2015-01-22 |newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-kobe-bryant-injury-20150123-story.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VmxSmAA6?url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-kobe-bryant-injury-20150123-story.html |archivedate=2015-01-23 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref><ref name=martin_11292015/><ref name=espn_01212016/>，其中有四年（2003、2011、2013、2016）是明星賽票選最高票<ref name=espn_01212016/>。柯比共四次獲選為[[NBA全明星賽最有價值球員|NBA全明星賽最有價值球員]]，和[[鲍勃·佩蒂特|鲍勃·佩蒂特]]共同保持紀錄<ref name=martin_11292015/>。他共入選[[NBA最佳阵容|NBA最佳阵容]]15次，追平賈霸和[[蒂姆·邓肯|蒂姆·邓肯]]原所保持的紀錄<ref>{{cite news |title=All-Time #NBArank: Players 11–15 |date=2016-02-10 |website=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/page/nbarank160205/all-nbarank-11-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fFbsnwHJ?url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/page/nbarank160205/all-nbarank-11-15 |archivedate=2016-02-12 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2020-02-01 }}</ref>，其中11次入選第一最佳阵容，追平[[卡爾·馬龍|卡爾·馬龍]]第二多的紀錄<ref>{{cite news |last=Trudell |first=Mike |title=Kobe Named All-NBA First Team ... Again |date=2013-05-23 |work=Lakers.com |url=http://blog.lakers.com/lakers/2013/05/23/kobe-named-all-nba-first-team-again/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GrTgopaX?url=http://blog.lakers.com/lakers/2013/05/23/kobe-named-all-nba-first-team-again/ |archivedate=2013-05-24 |dead-url=yes |access-date=2020-02-01 }}</ref>。柯比同時共12次入選[[NBA最佳防守陣容|NBA最佳防守陣容]]，僅次於邓肯的15次，其中柯比9次入選第一最佳防守陣容，追平由喬丹、[[凯文·加内特|凯文·加内特]]和[[加里·佩頓|加里·佩頓]]共同保持的紀錄<ref name=espn_11292015/><ref name=martin_11292015/>。柯比是聯盟史上第一位至少{{tsl|en|List of National Basketball Association seasons played leaders||出戰20個賽季}}的後衛<ref name=espn_11292015/>。他也在1997年以史上最年輕身分贏得[[NBA灌篮大赛|NBA灌篮大赛]]<ref name="bryanko01">{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/b/bryanko01.html|title=Kobe Bryant|work=basketball-reference.com|accessdate=2008-09-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67VEeNbPP?url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/b/bryanko01.html|archive-date=2012-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。柯比籃球生涯中，得分至少40分有121場，共創下大三元21次<ref name=lakers_11292015/>。

2020年2月15日，柯比[[#逝世|逝世]]後，NBA主席[[蕭華_(NBA)|蕭華]]宣布聯盟為了紀念柯比，將[[NBA全明星赛最有價值球員|NBA全明星赛最有價值球員]]改名為「[[NBA全明星賽柯比布萊恩最有價值球員|NBA全明星賽柯比布萊恩最有價值球員]]」<ref>{{cite news |author1=Tim Bontemps |title=NBA All-Star Game MVP award named in honor of Kobe Bryant |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28710867/nba-all-star-game-mvp-award-named-honor-kobe-bryant |accessdate=2020-02-17 |work=ESPN |date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217033615/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28710867/nba-all-star-game-mvp-award-named-honor-kobe-bryant |archive-date=2020-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月4日，柯比和[[蒂姆·鄧肯|蒂姆·鄧肯]]以及[[凱文·加內特|凱文·加內特]]等九人，入選2020年[[奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂|籃球名人堂]]入選名單<ref>{{cite web |title=Kobe Bryant, Tim Duncan, Kevin Garnett headline nine-member 2020 Hall of Fame Class |url=https://www.nba.com/hall-of-fame-class-of-2020-revealed |accessdate=2020-04-05 |work=NBA |date=2020-04-04 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111035447/https://www.nba.com/hall-of-fame-class-of-2020-revealed |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=徐崇哲(譯) |title=Kobe Bryant領銜入選2020籃球名人堂 鄧肯賈奈特同獲肯定 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004050002.aspx |accessdate=2020-05-26 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-04-05 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111035511/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004050002.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 球場外 ==
=== 個人生活 ===
[[File:Kobe_Bryant_at_Pirates_3_premiere.jpg|thumb]]》首映會]]
柯比是家中三位孩子年紀最輕的，他擁有兩位姐姐，夏莉亞（Sharia）和夏雅（Shaya），並和他們保持緊密的關係直到他逝世<ref name=":5">{{Citation|title=‘My name is Kobe Bryant’ – (1996) Kobe gives a class presentation on NBA vs. college|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5zr6Xm5IjPM|language=en|access-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224033516/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5zr6Xm5IjPM|archive-date=2020-02-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thegrio.com/2020/02/01/kobe-bryants-sisters-issue-statement-after-tragic-death-our-lives-are-forever-changed/|title=Kobe Bryant’s sisters issue statement after tragic death: ‘Our lives are forever changed’|last=Terrell|first=Ashley|date=2020-02-01|website=TheGrio|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224182841/https://thegrio.com/2020/02/01/kobe-bryants-sisters-issue-statement-after-tragic-death-our-lives-are-forever-changed/|archive-date=2020-02-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2020/01/28/kobe-bryants-sister-posts-touching-photo-tribute-to-late-brother/|title=Kobe Bryant’s sister posts touching photo tribute to late brother|last1=Nathan|first1=Sara|last2=Sheehy|first2=Kate|date=2020-01-28|website=New York Post|language=en|access-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129160951/https://nypost.com/2020/01/28/kobe-bryants-sister-posts-touching-photo-tribute-to-late-brother/|archive-date=2020-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1999年11月，年僅21歲的柯比和17歲在{{tsl|en|Tha Eastsidaz||Tha Eastsidaz}}音樂錄影帶《G'd Up》中擔任背景舞蹈演員的凡妮莎·雷恩（Vanessa Laine）相遇<ref name="rap">{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/On/Holly/Shows/Bryant/facts.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060219203516/http://www.eonline.com/On/Holly/Shows/Bryant/facts.html |archivedate=2006-02-19 |title=Everything You Need to Know About Kobe Bryant |accessdate=2007-10-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，柯比當時在大樓裡製作他的首張音樂專輯。兩人開始約會，並在半年後2000年5月訂婚<ref name="rap" />。由於凡妮莎仍然在加州[[亨廷頓比奇|亨廷頓比奇]]{{tsl|en|Marina High School (Huntington Beach, California)||Marina高中}}就讀，為了避免媒體審查，她透過獨立學習完成高中學位<ref name="rap" />。根據凡妮莎的表親萊拉·雷恩（Laila Laine）表示，兩人之間沒有[[婚前協議書|婚前協議書]]。凡妮莎說科比「太愛她了」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://allstarz.hollywood.com/kobe/vanessa02.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070406105500/http://allstarz.hollywood.com/kobe/vanessa02.htm |archivedate=2007-04-06 |first=Shawn |last=Hubler |title=Kobe's costar Vanessa Laine was just another sheltered teenager in Orange County. Then she fell in love with a phenomenon. |accessdate=2007-10-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2001年4月18日，他們在加州[[达纳角_(加利福尼亚州)|达纳角]]的天主教聖愛德華教堂結婚<ref>{{cite web|last=Keown|first=Tim|title=Isolation Play|publisher=ESPN|date=2003-09-01|url=http://www.espn.com/espnmag/story?id=3248290|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427003515/http://www.espn.com/espnmag/story?id=3248290|archive-date=2017-04-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Hubler|first=Shawn|title=Kobe's costar|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=2005-02-15|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2005/feb/15/entertainment/et-vanessa15/3|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427003658/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/feb/15/entertainment/et-vanessa15/3|archive-date=2017-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。柯比的雙親、他的兩位姊姊、他的長期顧問經紀人阿恩·泰勒姆（Arn Tellem）或他的湖人隊友都沒有參加婚禮。科比的父母出於多種原因反對此段婚姻。根據報導，科比的父母對於他年紀輕輕就結婚感到疑慮，尤其結婚對象並非為非裔美國人{{notetag|凡妮莎的父親是墨西哥裔和意大利裔，母親則是墨西哥裔和菲律賓裔<ref>{{cite news |title=Cupcake Magazine interview with Vanessa Bryant |url=http://www.cupcakemag.com/2012/07/behind-the-famous-name-our-chat-with-vanessa-bryant/ |accessdate=2020-02-01 |work=cupcakemag |date=2013-07-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701005437/http://www.cupcakemag.com/2012/07/behind-the-famous-name-our-chat-with-vanessa-bryant/ |archivedate=2013-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。}}<ref name="rap" />。這個分歧導致柯比與雙親之間產生疏遠，直到夫妻倆的第一個女兒誕生才結束<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.com/kobe-bryant-divorce-kobe-and-vanessa-through-years-photos-553607|title=Kobe Bryant Divorce: Kobe and Vanessa Through the Years [PHOTOS]|date=2011-12-17|website=International Business Times|access-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822144156/https://www.ibtimes.com/kobe-bryant-divorce-kobe-and-vanessa-through-years-photos-553607|archive-date=2019-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

柯比的第一個小孩納塔莉亞（Natalia）出生於2003年1月<ref>{{cite web|magazine=US Magazine|title=Kobe Bryant's Sweetest Moments With His Wife Vanessa Bryant and 4 Daughters: Pics|date=2020-01-26|last=Cardoza|first=Riley|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-moms/pictures/kobe-bryants-sweetest-moments-with-his-wife-daughters-pics/|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131101424/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-moms/pictures/kobe-bryants-sweetest-moments-with-his-wife-daughters-pics/|archive-date=2020-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這幫助科比和他的父母和解。2005年春天，凡妮莎因為[[異位妊娠|異位妊娠]]而[[流产|流产]]。他們的第二個小孩吉安娜（Gianna）出生於2006年5月<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/new/xmlfeed.nsf/mndwebpages/shaq%20is%20a%20dad%20six%20minutes%20after%20kobe_02_05_2006|title=Shaq is a Dad Six Minutes After Kobe|website=Contact Music|date=2006-05-02|accessdate=2007-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416235742/http://www.contactmusic.com/new/xmlfeed.nsf/mndwebpages/shaq%20is%20a%20dad%20six%20minutes%20after%20kobe_02_05_2006|archive-date=2009-04-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年12月16日，凡妮莎提出離婚，理由是雙方不可調和<ref>{{cite news | url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/12/kobe-bryant-divorce-vanessa-cites-irreconcilable-difference.html | title=Kobe Bryant divorce: Vanessa cites 'irreconcilable differences' | last=Kim | first=Victoria | newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | date=2011-12-16 | accessdate=2011-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108082844/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/12/kobe-bryant-divorce-vanessa-cites-irreconcilable-difference.html | archive-date=2012-01-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/12/kobe-bryant-divorce-vanessa-lakers-star-will-share-custody-of-daughters.html | work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | title=L.A. Now | date=2011-12-16 | access-date=2020-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126225002/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/12/kobe-bryant-divorce-vanessa-lakers-star-will-share-custody-of-daughters.html | archive-date=2020-01-26 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年1月11日，科比和他的妻子都透過[[社会化媒体|社交媒體]]宣布他們已取消離婚<ref>{{cite web|title=Kobe Bryant, wife Vanessa call off their divorce|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-400_162-57563631/kobe-bryant-wife-vanessa-call-off-their-divorce/|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112074852/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-400_162-57563631/kobe-bryant-wife-vanessa-call-off-their-divorce/|archive-date=2013-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年12月上旬，凡妮莎生下他們的第三個女兒畢安卡（Bianka）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/celebrity/kobe-bryant-wife-vanessa-welcome-234000119.html |title=Kobe Bryant and Wife Vanessa Welcome Third Child |last=Drysdale |first=Jennifer |date=2016-12-08 |website=Yahoo! |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422050625/https://www.yahoo.com/celebrity/kobe-bryant-wife-vanessa-welcome-234000119.html |archive-date=2017-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/nba/news/kobe-bryant-welcomes-his-3rd-child/vlxtknrf27fjz9igcw4l4mb9 |title=Kobe Bryant welcomes his third child |last=Harris |first=Sarah Jane |date=2016-12-08 |website=sportingnews.com |access-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626220448/http://www.sportingnews.com/nba/news/kobe-bryant-welcomes-his-3rd-child/vlxtknrf27fjz9igcw4l4mb9 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.etonline.com/news/205700_kobe_bryant_shares_adorable_first_pic_of_newborn_daughter_bianka|title=Kobe Bryant Shares Adorable First Pic of Newborn Daughter Bianka|publisher=Entertainment Tonight|date=2016-12-21|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224064123/http://www.etonline.com/news/205700_kobe_bryant_shares_adorable_first_pic_of_newborn_daughter_bianka|archive-date=2017-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且在2019年6月，夫妻倆迎接他們的第四個女兒卡布莉（Capri）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.com/parents/kobe-bryant-daughter-capri-kobe-first-photo/|date=2019-07-04|magazine=People|last=Adams|first=Char|title=Meet Baby 'KoKo!' Kobe Bryant Officially Introduces His 'Little Princess' — Daughter Capri Kobe|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127123644/https://people.com/parents/kobe-bryant-daughter-capri-kobe-first-photo/|archive-date=2020-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-moms/news/kobe-bryants-wife-vanessa-gives-birth-welcomes-4th-daughter/|title=Kobe Bryant's Wife Vanessa Gives Birth, Welcomes Fourth Daughter|work=Us Weekly|date=2019-06-21|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717010009/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-moms/news/kobe-bryants-wife-vanessa-gives-birth-welcomes-4th-daughter/|archive-date=2019-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

科比是一名虔誠的天主教徒。他說該信仰和牧師幫助他度過艱難的時期，例如對[[#性侵案|性侵案]]的審判。一位天主教徒{{tsl|en|cantor||領唱}}說，她受到科比的信仰以及他對她的尊重<ref name=":2" /><ref name="cna" /><ref name=":3">{{cite web|url=http://aleteia.org/2016/04/15/kobe-bryant-saved-by-his-catholic-faith/|title=Remembering Kobe Bryant: Formed and saved by his Catholic faith|last=Kosloski|first=Philip|date=2016-04-15|accessdate=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330203521/https://aleteia.org/2016/04/15/kobe-bryant-saved-by-his-catholic-faith/|archive-date=2019-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。科比和他的家人會固定前往位於[[新港滩|新港滩]]的天神之后教堂（Our Lady Queen of Angels Catholic Church）。科比[[#逝世|因飛機墜毀而逝世]]的前幾個小時，他才與吉安娜在那一起接受[[聖餐禮|聖餐禮]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://abc7news.com/5884317/|title=Before fatal flight, Kobe and daughter attended California church, took communion, priest says|date=2020-01-28|website=ABC7 San Francisco|language=en|access-date=2020-01-28|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509205013/https://abc7news.com/5884317/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://meaww.com/kobe-bryant-private-funeral-service-likely-same-catholic-church-he-went-before-boarding-chopper|title=Kobe Bryant's private funeral service likely at same Catholic church he went before boarding chopper|website=meaww.com|access-date=2020-02-29|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510174941/https://meaww.com/kobe-bryant-private-funeral-service-likely-same-catholic-church-he-went-before-boarding-chopper|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

科比會說多種語言，其中他精通英文、意大利文和西班牙文<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Citation|title=Una scuola di basket per futuri campioni: la promessa di Kobe Bryant nell'intervista a Reggio Emilia|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gmGOZkIzN8|language=en|access-date=2020-01-29|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417165742/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gmGOZkIzN8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Kobe Bryant agradece a los latinos en español|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEojYCnn9Zs|language=en|access-date=2020-01-29|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417165759/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEojYCnn9Zs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com.mx/los-angeles/nota/_/id/2243842/kobe-no-imagine-este-nivel |title=Kobe: "No imaginé este nivel" |first=Gonzalo |last=Aguirregomezcorta |website=ESPN Mexico |access-date=2015-11-30 |date=2014-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208065954/http://www.espn.com.mx/los-angeles/nota/_/id/2243842/kobe-no-imagine-este-nivel |archive-date=2015-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com.mx/los-angeles/nota/_/id/2539723/kobe-bryant-tras-anunciar-su-retiro-ahora-me-siento-relajado |title=Kobe Bryant tras anunciar su retiro: "Ahora me siento relajado" |first=Gonzalo |last=Aguirregomezcorta |website=ESPN Mexico |access-date=2015-11-30 |date=2015-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208043344/http://www.espn.com.mx/los-angeles/nota/_/id/2539723/kobe-bryant-tras-anunciar-su-retiro-ahora-me-siento-relajado |archive-date=2015-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科比為自己的綽號取為「[[黑曼巴|黑曼巴]]」（BLACK MAMBA），是因為他希望自己的籃球技術能模仿[[黑曼巴|黑曼巴]]的能力<ref name=LATimes2008>{{cite news|last=Crowe|first=Jerry|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/may/23/sports/sp-crowe23|title=Text messages from press row ...|date=2008-05-23|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2010-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110314201605/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/may/23/sports/sp-crowe23|archive-date=2011-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://lakersblog.latimes.com/lakersblog/2011/01/kobe-bryant-and-robert-rodriguez-hype-ads-6-minute-film-at-nike-vault-1.html|title=Kobe Bryant and, Robert Rodriguez talk about Black Mamba Nike ads, six-minute film|date=2011-01-31|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023120135/http://lakersblog.latimes.com/lakersblog/2011/01/kobe-bryant-and-robert-rodriguez-hype-ads-6-minute-film-at-nike-vault-1.html|archive-date=2018-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2012-13賽季，他開始稱自己為「葡萄酒」，描述他的籃球打法[[葡萄酒的陳化|像優質葡萄酒一樣老化]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/36373/rapid-reaction-lakers-113-trail-blazers-106|title=Rapid Reaction: Lakers 113, Trail Blazers 106|last=McMenamin|first=Dave|date=2013-04-11|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Fo4kr0lu?url=http://espn.go.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/36373/rapid-reaction-lakers-113-trail-blazers-106|archivedate=2013-04-11|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2020-01-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/mar/03/sports/la-sp-0304-lakers-hawks-20130304|title=Kobe Bryant and Lakers soar to new heights (or at least .500)|last=Bresnahan|first=Mike|date=2013-03-03|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FoGf2VEi?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/mar/03/sports/la-sp-0304-lakers-hawks-20130304|archivedate=2013-04-11|accessdate=2020-01-31}}</ref>。

2002年1月，科比以400萬美元買下一棟位於{{le|新港海岸 (新港灘)|Newport Coast, Newport Beach|新港海岸}}[[死路|死路]]的{{tsl|en|Mediterranean Revival architecture||地中海風格}}房子<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZNAdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2KcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6703,744809|title=Kobe Bryant Buys Home For More Than $4 million|date=|accessdate=2011-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725030643/http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZNAdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2KcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6703,744809|archive-date=2013-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在2015年5月將房子賣掉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/realestate/hot-property/la-fi-hotprop-kobe-bryant-sale-20150529-story.html|title=Kobe Bryant sets price record with Newport Coast home sale|date=2015-05-29|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126225033/https://www.latimes.com/business/realestate/hot-property/la-fi-hotprop-kobe-bryant-sale-20150529-story.html|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年，科比與拍卖行在法律上存在分歧，因為他的母親將他早年的物品拍賣，並從中獲得45萬美元。母親辯稱科比已授予她對他留在家中物品的權利。但是科比的律師要求拍賣行完整歸還物品<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9238503/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-battles-mom-nj-business-auction|title=Kobe Bryant, mom in court battle|date=2013-05-03|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GLro2qsD?url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9238503/kobe-bryant-los-angeles-lakers-battles-mom-nj-business-auction|archivedate=2013-05-04|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2020-01-31}}</ref>。在預定的審判前雙方已達成和解，允許拍賣行出售低於10％的物品。科比的父母在書面聲明中表示對於誤解他感到歉意，並感謝科比多年來給予他們的經濟支持<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/Kobe-Bryant-Goldin-Auction-Settlement-210820051.html|title=Kobe Wins Battle to Prevent Mom From Auctioning His Stuff|last1=Stamm|first1=Dan|accessdate=2013-06-10|publisher=NBC 10 Philadelphia|agency=Associated Press|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928031849/http://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/Kobe-Bryant-Goldin-Auction-Settlement-210820051.html|archive-date=2013-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9360162/kobe-bryant-memorabilia-lawsuit-settled-parents-apologize|title=Deal reached in Kobe Bryant case|last=Rovell|first=Darren|date=2013-06-10|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HHUePiWh?url=http://espn.go.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/9360162/kobe-bryant-memorabilia-lawsuit-settled-parents-apologize|archivedate=2013-06-10|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2020-01-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/9360162/kobe-bryant-memorabilia-lawsuit-settled-parents-apologize|title=Kobe auction suit settled; parents apologize|date=2013-06-10|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126225556/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/9360162/kobe-bryant-memorabilia-lawsuit-settled-parents-apologize|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

科比是他的家鄉球隊[[费城老鹰|费城老鹰]]的終生球迷<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.phillyvoice.com/kobe-im-staying-eagles-fan-despite-la-team/|title=Kobe: I'm staying an Eagles fan despite L.A. team | PhillyVoice|access-date=2020-01-31|date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126224949/https://www.phillyvoice.com/kobe-im-staying-eagles-fan-despite-la-team/|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]、[[AC米兰|AC米兰]]和[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼彻斯特城]]的足球迷<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-fc-yahoo/kobe-bryant-credits-court-vision-to-soccer-171433623.html|title=Kobe Bryant credits soccer for his extraordinary basketball court vision|date=2016-01-09|author=Ahmed, Sahahan|publisher=[[雅虎|雅虎]]|website=sports.yahoo.com|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114192321/https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-fc-yahoo/kobe-bryant-credits-court-vision-to-soccer-171433623.html|archive-date=2020-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobile.twitter.com/mancity/status/923862364570771464?lang=en|title=Mamba Mentality|publisher=[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部]]|website=twitter.com|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218152442/https://mobile.twitter.com/mancity/status/923862364570771464?lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》，科比從NBA退休前共賺進6.8億美元<ref name="Career Earnings">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2015/11/30/kobe-bryant-will-retire-with-record-680-million-in-career-earnings/|title=Kobe Bryant Will Retire With Record $680 Million In Career Earnings|last=Badenhausen|first=Kurt|website=Forbes|language=en|access-date=2020-02-24|date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227004242/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2015/11/30/kobe-bryant-will-retire-with-record-680-million-in-career-earnings/|archive-date=2019-12-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 性侵案 ====
2003年夏天，科羅拉多[[伊格爾縣_(科羅拉多州)|伊格爾郡]]警方逮捕了科比，因为一位19岁的旅館女服务生报警称被性侵。科比入住该旅館以等待在附近预约的膝盖手术，该女子称在手术前科比在旅馆房间強姦了她。科比交保候审期间与妻子凡妮莎一起召開記者会，承認与该女子发生了婚外性行为，向妻子和公众道歉，但否认性侵，坚称性行为发生的时候双方是自愿的<ref>{{cite news |last=SI Staff |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2003/basketball/nba/12/26/kobe.interview.ap/index.html?cnn-yes |date=2003-12-23 |title=Bryant distracted, scared amid sex assault case |agency=Associated Press |work=Sports Illustrated |accessdate=2007-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040906074827/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2003/basketball/nba/12/26/kobe.interview.ap/index.html?cnn-yes |archive-date=2004-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/lakers/2004-02-12-shaq-kobe_x.htm |title=Shaq, Kobe still main keys to Lakers' fortunes |first=David Leon |last=Moore |date=2004-02-12 |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |accessdate=2007-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101116031529/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/lakers/2004-02-12-shaq-kobe_x.htm |archive-date=2010-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该事件使科比的公众形象大受打击。[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]和[[能多益|能多益]]解除了科比的代言合約，科比的球衣销量也因此一落千丈<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,143646,00.html |title=Fans Shunning Kobe Bryant's Jersey – Celebrity Gossip | Entertainment News | Arts And Entertainment |publisher=Fox News |date=2005-01-07 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100523093402/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,143646,00.html |archive-date=2010-05-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。但2004年9月，因为该女子拒绝在法庭[[宣誓|宣誓]]，因此控方撤销了对科比的指控。随后科比发表公开声明，向该女子道歉并承认错误，在声明中他说<ref name="sfgate_dismissal">{{cite news |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/c/a/2004/09/02/MNG6E8IB861.DTL |title=Bryant rape case ends in dismissal |first=T.R. |last=Reid |date=2004-09-02 |accessdate=2007-10-16 |newspaper=[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071112212732/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2004%2F09%2F02%2FMNG6E8IB861.DTL |archive-date=2007-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Prosecutors Drop Kobe Bryant Rape Case |author=Kirk Johnson |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/09/02/national/02kobe.html?_r=1 |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |date=2004-09-02 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828104622/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/09/02/national/02kobe.html?_r=1 |archive-date=2011-08-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>：

{{cquote|虽然我坚信当时我们双方都是自愿的，但是我现在了解到她的感受和我不同，近几个月她的律师和她传递的信息告诉我她当时的感受，她当时并不同意这一行为。}}

该女子同时向科比发起[[民事诉讼|民事诉讼]]，最终双方私下和解<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/7019659/ns/bryant_sexual_assault_lawsuit//|title=Suit Settlement Ends Bryant Saga|publisher=Associated Press via [[NBC體育|NBC體育]]|date=2005-03-03|access-date=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126085517/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/7019659/ns/bryant_sexual_assault_lawsuit/|archive-date=2012-01-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 代言 ===
[[File:NikeTaipeiFlagshipStoreLaunch_Main.jpg|thumb]]
在開始[[1996-97_NBA赛季|1996-97 NBA赛季]]之前，科比與[[愛迪達|愛迪達]]簽署一份為期六年約4,800萬美元合約<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-7226901_ITM |title=Article: Basketball Star Leaps into Global Ventures |publisher=AccessMyLibrary |date=2000-06-16 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |first=Mike |last=Jensen |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120720151100/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/article-1G1-122056585/basketball-star-leaps-into.html |archive-date=2012-07-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-8828547_ITM |title=Information and results for 'Adidas, Basketball Star Kobe Bryant Part Ways.' |publisher=AccessMyLibrary |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120719142955/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/article-1G1-268476944/nike-and-adidas-prepare.html |archive-date=2012-07-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的第一個簽名鞋是Equipment KB8<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/article/35398 |title=Adidas Airs Out New Kobe Bryant Shoe, Ad Campaign |publisher=Sportsbusinessdaily.com |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100306202348/http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/article/35398 |archive-date=2010-03-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科比的其他早期代言包括與[[可口可乐公司|可口可乐公司]]簽約以代言他們的[[雪碧|雪碧]]飲料，這出現在[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]的廣告中、推廣[[斯伯丁|斯伯丁]]的全新NBA使用球、{{tsl|en|Upper Deck Company||上甲板}}、意大利巧克力公司[[佛列羅|佛列羅]]旗下品牌[[能多益|能多益]]、{{tsl|en|Russell Corporation||羅素公司}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Badenhausen |first=Kurt |url=https://www.forbes.com/2004/09/03/cz_kb_0903kobe.html |title=Kobe Bryant's Sponsorship Will Rebound |work=Forbes |date=2004-03-09 |accessdate=2008-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210190505/http://www.forbes.com/2004/09/03/cz_kb_0903kobe.html |archive-date=2009-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並出現在[[任天堂|任天堂]]屬於自己的系列電子遊戲中。許多公司如麥當勞和佛列羅在[[#性侵案|性侵案]]發生後終止與科比的合約<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/22/sports/sp-kobe22 | work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | title=Bryant will lose out again to Big Three | first=Greg | last=Johnson | date=2008-06-22 | accessdate=2010-05-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090622092452/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/22/sports/sp-kobe22 | archive-date=2009-06-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。值得注意的是[[耐克|耐克]]，在[[#性侵案|性侵案]]發生前和柯比簽訂為期五年4–4.5億美元的合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://advertising.about.com/od/kobebryant/a/bryantsendorse.htm |title=Kobe Bryant's Endorsement Deals |publisher=Advertising.about.com |date=2010-04-15 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203153519/http://advertising.about.com/od/kobebryant/a/bryantsendorse.htm |archive-date=2010-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Nike">{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-07-10-kobe-bryant_x.htm |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |title=Kobe Bryant resumes endorsement career |date=2005-07-10 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628213605/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-07-10-kobe-bryant_x.htm |archive-date=2011-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，當年他們拒絕使用他的圖像或推銷他的新鞋，但在兩年後他的形象逐漸恢復，耐克最終開始推廣科比<ref name="Nike" />。此後，他通過子公司{{tsl|en|Energy Brands||Energy Brands}}恢復與[[可口可乐公司|可口可乐公司]]的代言合約<ref>{{cite web |last=Salazar-Moreno |first=Quibian |url=http://www.bvonsports.com/2008/05/12/endorsements-coming-back-to-kobe-bryant/ |title=Endorsements Coming Back to Kobe Bryant |publisher=Blackvoices |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727100859/http://www.bvonsports.com/2008/05/12/endorsements-coming-back-to-kobe-bryant/ |archive-date=2013-07-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科比還是《{{tsl|en|NBA 07||NBA '07: Featuring the Life Vol. 2}}》的封面運動員，并且出演了2008年遊戲《[[吉他英雄：世界巡演|吉他英雄：世界巡演]]》（與[[東尼·霍克_(運動員)|東尼·霍克]]、[[迈克尔·菲尔普斯|迈克尔·菲尔普斯]]和[[艾力士·羅德里奎茲|艾力士·羅德里奎茲]]一起）和2010年遊戲《[[決勝時刻：黑色行動|決勝時刻：黑色行動]]》（與[[吉米·坎摩爾|吉米·坎摩爾]]）的廣告<ref name="COD">{{cite web |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/nba/blog/ball_dont_lie/post/Kobe-Bryant-shoots-em-up-in-new-Call-of-Duty-?urn=nba-282854 |title=Kobe Bryant shoots 'em up in new 'Call of Duty' ad |first=Dan |last=Devine |work={{tsl|en|Yahoo! Sports||Sports.Yahoo.com}} |date=2010-11-05 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629063709/http://sports.yahoo.com/nba/blog/ball_dont_lie/post/Kobe-Bryant-shoots-em-up-in-new-Call-of-Duty-?urn=nba-282854 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2008年宣傳耐克Hyperdunk球鞋的影片中，科比似乎靠原地起跳飞越了高速迎面驶来的[[阿斯顿·马丁|阿斯顿·马丁]]跑车，此特技被認為是假的。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》表示，真正的特技可能會違反科比與湖人的合約<ref>{{cite news |title=No, Kobe Bryant Did Not Jump Over a Car |date=2008-04-15 |agency=rankingsandreviews.com |work=[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]] |url=http://usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/cars-trucks/daily-news/080415-120429/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5y5cKyN5V?url=http://usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/cars-trucks/daily-news/080415-120429/ |archivedate=2011-04-20 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2020-01-31 }}</ref>。在推廣完耐克的Hyperdunk鞋之後，科比推出耐克的第四代簽名系列Zoom Kobe IV。2010年，耐克推出另一雙鞋Nike Zoom Kobe V<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tradingmarkets.com/.site/news/Stock%20News/2711325/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101218220052/http://www.tradingmarkets.com/.site/news/Stock%20News/2711325/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2010-12-18 |title=Nike launches Nike Zoom Kobe V with Kobe Bryant |publisher=TradingMarkets.com |date=2009-12-09 |accessdate=2010-06-08 }}</ref>。2009年，科比與Nubeo簽約以推廣“ Black Mamba系列”的販售<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.upscalehype.com/2009/10/kobe-bryant-wearing-nubeo-black-mamba-mvp-watch/ |title=Kobe Bryant Wearing Nubeo Black Mamba MVP Watch "UpscaleHype |publisher=Upscalehype.com |accessdate=2010-06-08 |date=2009-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623110051/http://www.upscalehype.com/2009/10/kobe-bryant-wearing-nubeo-black-mamba-mvp-watch/ |archive-date=2010-06-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2009年2月9日，科比登上《{{tsl|en|ESPN The Magazine||ESPN 雜誌}}》封面，但是這與籃球無關，這是關於科比成為[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那足球俱乐部]]的忠實粉絲<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espnmag/fanIssue |title=Kobe Bryant ESPN The Magazine Fan Issue |accessdate=2009-05-15 |magazine=ESPN The Magazine |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090531085241/http://sports.espn.go.com/espnmag/fanissue |archivedate=2009-05-31 }}</ref>。[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]估計，科比在2007年代言費總共1600萬美元<ref>{{cite news | url=http://money.cnn.com/galleries/2007/fortune/0711/gallery.endorsements.fortune/6.html | title=Top 10 endorsement superstars | publisher=CNN | accessdate=2010-05-07 | date=2008-12-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100301094223/http://money.cnn.com/galleries/2007/fortune/0711/gallery.endorsements.fortune/6.html | archive-date=2010-03-01 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，科比以身價4,800萬美元在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》全球薪水最高的運動員名單中僅次於老虎伍茲和喬丹<ref>{{cite news |author1=Kritchever, Patrick |title=The Forbes Celebrity 100 |url=https://www.forbes.com/lists/2010/53/celeb-100-10_Kobe-Bryant_OKPF.html |accessdate=2010-07-13 |work=[[福布斯|福布斯]] |date=2010-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723085808/http://www.forbes.com/lists/2010/53/celeb-100-10_Kobe-Bryant_OKPF.html |archive-date=2010-07-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Kobe_Bryant_in_2008.jpg|thumb]]，柯比陪同時任美國總統[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]、[[贾森·基德|贾森·基德]]和[[德隆·威廉姆斯|德隆·威廉姆斯]]]]
2010年12月13日，科比與[[土耳其航空|土耳其航空]]簽署了為期兩年的合約<ref>{{cite web |last=Rovell |first=Darren |url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/40641746/Kobe_Bryant_To_Endorse_Turkish_Airlines |title=Kobe Bryant To Endorse Turkish Airlines |accessdate=2011-02-23 |work=CNBC.com |quote=It's a two-year deal that will involve Bryant starring in a promotional film that will be aired on international television channels and in movie theatres in more than 80 countries next year. |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015015604/http://www.cnbc.com/id/40641746/Kobe_Bryant_To_Endorse_Turkish_Airlines |archivedate=2012-10-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Li |first=Shan |title=Kobe Bryant's Turkish Airlines deal outrages Armenian Americans |date=2010-12-16 |newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/16/local/la-me-kobe-bryant-armenian-20101216 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310094559/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/16/local/la-me-kobe-bryant-armenian-20101216 |archive-date=2011-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=The first Kobe Bryant Turkish Airlines commercial has landed |date=2011-02-28 |work=NBC Sports |url=http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2011/02/28/the-first-kobe-bryant-turkish-airlines-commercial-has-landed/ |accessdate=2011-02-23 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110303071204/http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2011/02/28/the-first-kobe-bryant-turkish-airlines-commercial-has-landed/ |archivedate=2011-03-03 }}</ref>。

2012年9月，科比與[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那足球俱乐部]]球星[[利昂内尔·梅西|利昂内尔·梅西]]一起為[[土耳其航空|土耳其航空]]拍攝廣告。在廣告中，二人為了贏得一位小男孩的注意而競爭<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ruav0KvQOOg|title=Kobe vs Messi: Legends on Board – Turkish Airlines|publisher=Turkish Airlines|date=2012-12-06|accessdate=2012-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416030915/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ruav0KvQOOg|archive-date=2019-04-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》將科比列為全球第五高薪體育球星，僅次於[[弗洛伊德·梅威瑟|弗洛伊德·梅威瑟]]、[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]、[[勒布朗·詹姆斯|勒布朗·詹姆斯]]和利昂内尔·梅西<ref>{{cite news |title="LeBron James: Cleveland Cavaliers return for NBA star" |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/basketball/28272054 |accessdate=2014-07-11 |work=BBC |date=2014-07-12 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524151848/https://www.bbc.com/sport/basketball/28272054 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科比為下列遊戲的封面運動員：
* ''{{tsl|en|Kobe Bryant in NBA Courtside||Kobe Bryant in NBA Courtside}}''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/kobe-bryant-in-nba-courtside |title=Kobe Bryant in NBA Courtside for Nintendo 64 |publisher=MobyGames |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100124063050/http://www.mobygames.com/game/kobe-bryant-in-nba-courtside |archive-date=2010-01-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
