* ''[[NBA_2K21|NBA 2K21]]（永懷曼巴版）''

科比還是[[2019年国际篮联篮球世界杯|2019年国际篮联篮球世界杯]]中國區的全球大使之一<ref>{{cite web |url=https://in.nba.com/news/fiba-basketball-world-cup-2019-dirk-nowitzki-named-as-third-global-ambassador-joining-kobe-bryant-and-yao-ming/114s1jn4cbtm91w5f2ufq8zg6b |title=FIBA Basketball World Cup 2019: Dirk Nowitzki named as third global ambassador joining Kobe Bryant and Yao Ming |work=NBA.com |date=2019-05-16 |accessdate=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190516224424/https://in.nba.com/news/fiba-basketball-world-cup-2019-dirk-nowitzki-named-as-third-global-ambassador-joining-kobe-bryant-and-yao-ming/114s1jn4cbtm91w5f2ufq8zg6b |archive-date=2019-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 其他 ===
*2011年，柯比與同是雪碧旗下代言人的歌手[[周杰倫|周杰倫]]合演[[雪碧|雪碧汽水]]廣告，並合唱廣告曲《天地一鬥》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.cri.cn/6666/2011/02/23/1261s622251.htm |title=CRI.com: Kobe Bryant Works with Jay Chou in New Song |publisher= |date=2011-02-23 |accessdate=2011-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110505063248/http://english.cri.cn/6666/2011/02/23/1261s622251.htm |archive-date=2011-05-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Daniel |last=Gilroy |url=http://advertising.chinasmack.com/2011/sprite-china-kobe-bryant-jay-chou-music-video.html |title=ChinaSmack: Sprite China – Kobe Bryant and Jay Chou music video " 天地一鬥 " ("Tian Di Yi Dou") with Jay Chou feat. Kobe Bryant |publisher=Advertising.chinasmack.com |date=2011-02-23 |accessdate=2011-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423150042/http://advertising.chinasmack.com/2011/sprite-china-kobe-bryant-jay-chou-music-video.html |archive-date=2011-04-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；音樂的營利全數捐贈給貧困學校用於加強籃球設施<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.popasia.net/jay-chou-releases-mv-with-kobe-bryant/ |title=Jay Chou releases MV with Kobe Bryant |publisher=PopAsia |date= |accessdate=2011-06-16 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324154348/http://www.popasia.net/jay-chou-releases-mv-with-kobe-bryant/ |archivedate=2012-03-24 }}</ref>。
*2018年，其编剧及旁白配音的动画短片《[[亲爱的篮球|亲爱的篮球]]》获得[[奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖|奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖]]，史上第一次有NBA球星獲頒小金人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/awards/2018/03/04/oscars-kobe-bryant-dear-basketball/|title=Kobe Bryant is officially an Oscar winner|magazine=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|first=Dana|last=Schwartz|date=2018-03-04|access-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626193118/https://ew.com/awards/2018/03/04/oscars-kobe-bryant-dear-basketball/|archive-date=2019-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://oscar.go.com/nominees/short-film-animated/|title=90th Academy Award Animated Short Film Nominees|website=The Oscars 2018|publisher=[[The_Walt_Disney_Company|The Walt Disney Company]]|date=2018-01-23|accessdate=2018-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124070653/http://oscar.go.com/nominees/short-film-animated|archive-date=2018-01-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 逝世 ==
{{main|2020年卡拉巴萨斯S-76B坠毁事故}}
[[Image:Kobe_Bryant_Staples_Center_Memorial-01_2020-01-28.jpg|thumb]]
[[太平洋时区|洛杉磯時間]]2020年1月26日上午9時6分，一架[[賽考斯基S-76精靈直升機|賽考斯基S-76精靈直升機]]搭載柯比、他的二女兒吉安娜、大學棒球教練{{tsl|en|John Altobelli||約翰·阿爾托貝利}}、機師等等共九名人員，從[[橙縣_(加利福尼亞州)|橙縣]][[約翰韋恩機場|約翰韋恩機場]]飛離<ref name="9 on board">{{cite news |last1=Winton |first1=Richard |title=Kobe Bryant, daughter Gianna among nine dead in helicopter crash in Calabasas |url=https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas |accessdate=2020-01-26 |work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |date=2020-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126212423/https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas |archive-date=2020-01-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Death-CNBC">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/01/26/kobe-bryant-killed-in-helicopter-crash-reports-say.html|title=NBA superstar Kobe Bryant and his daughter Gianna killed in LA-area helicopter crash|first1=Emma|last1=Newburger|first2=Jabari|last2=Young|date=2020-01-26|website=CNBC|access-date=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128061805/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/01/26/kobe-bryant-killed-in-helicopter-crash-reports-say.html|archive-date=2020-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas|title=Kobe Bryant, daughter Gianna among nine dead in helicopter crash in Calabasas|date=2020-01-26|website=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126212423/https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/us/live-news/kobe-bryant-dies-in-helicopter-crash/index.html|title=Kobe Bryant was one of five people killed in a helicopter crash in Calabasas, California|last=Alfonso|first=Fernando|last2=Vera|first2=Amir|date=2020-01-26|website=CNN|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-01-26|archive-date=2021-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223140505/https://www.cnn.com/us/live-news/kobe-bryant-dies-in-helicopter-crash/index.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28569415/the-nba-world-mourns-death-kobe-bryant|title=NBA, sports worlds mourn the death of Kobe Bryant|date=2020-01-26|website=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|access-date=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127080719/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28569415/the-nba-world-mourns-death-kobe-bryant|archive-date=2020-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。飛行的目的地為位於[[千橡市_(加利福尼亞州)|千橡市]]由柯比的曼巴基金會所舉辦的籃球比賽<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/kobe-bryant-death-map-shows-flight-path-before-fatal-crash-2020-1|title=This map shows the exact path of Kobe Bryant's helicopter before it crashed, killing all 9 people on board|first=Will|last=Martin|website=Business Insider|date=2020-01-27|accessdate=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128151448/https://www.businessinsider.com/kobe-bryant-death-map-shows-flight-path-before-fatal-crash-2020-1|archive-date=2020-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

當天早晨當地天氣為小雨和大霧，[[洛杉矶警察局|洛杉矶警察局]]的直升機<ref name=":1" />和大多數其他空中載具因此停飛<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=https://www.tmz.com/2020/01/26/kobe-bryant-killed-dead-helicopter-crash-in-calabasas/|title=Kobe Bryant & Daughter Die in Helicopter Crash, Photos from Her Last Game|website=TMZ|language=en|access-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126195700/https://www.tmz.com/2020/01/26/kobe-bryant-killed-dead-helicopter-crash-in-calabasas/|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。飛行跟踪器顯示，由於該地區空中交通繁忙，直升機在{{tsl|en|Los Angeles Zoo||洛杉磯動物園}}上方{{convert|850|feet}}的高空盤旋六圈。上午9時30分，機師聯繫[[好莱坞伯班克机场|好莱坞伯班克机场]]的塔台<ref name=":0" />，回應塔台告知他「飛得太低了，無法被雷達追踪」的情況<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/nba/news/36226/11919276/kobe-bryant-pilot-warned-youre-too-low-seconds-before-helicopter-crashed-in-fog|title=Kobe Bryant: Pilot warned 'you're too low' seconds before helicopter crashed in fog|website=Sky Sports|access-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128052739/https://www.skysports.com/nba/news/36226/11919276/kobe-bryant-pilot-warned-youre-too-low-seconds-before-helicopter-crashed-in-fog|archive-date=2020-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時直升機遇上大霧，並轉往南方飛行。上午9時40分，直升機以{{convert|161|knots}}的速度從{{convert|1200|ft|}}迅速爬升至{{convert|2000|ft|}}<ref name=":0" />。上午9時45分，直升機墜落於洛杉磯市中心西北約{{convert|30|mi}}的[[卡拉巴萨斯|卡拉巴萨斯]]地區。科比、他的二女兒吉安娜和其他七位機上人員全數罹難<ref name=":0" />。初步報告指出，直升機在大霧中墜毀於卡拉巴薩斯上方的山<ref name="LATDeath">{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas|title=Kobe Bryant is killed in helicopter crash in Calabasas|author1=Winton, Richard|first2=Dan|last2=Woike|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|date=2020-01-26|accessdate=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126212423/https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2020-01-26/aircraft-slams-into-hillside-explodes-in-flames-near-calabasas|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Source: Kobe among dead in helicopter crash |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28569438/kobe-bryant-dead-helicopter-crash |work=ESPN.com |date=2020-01-26 |access-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129230621/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28569438/kobe-bryant-dead-helicopter-crash |archive-date=2020-01-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現場目擊證人表示當時有聽到直升機在墜毀前掙扎的聲音<ref name="auto" />。

由於直升機沒有裝載[[飛行紀錄儀|飛行紀錄儀]]，墜機的原因仍然未知。[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]、[[國家運輸安全委員會|國家運輸安全委員會]]和[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]<ref name=":1" />已著手展開調查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/california-helicopter-crash-calabasas-brush-fire-fatalities-reported|title=Kobe Bryant among those killed in California helicopter crash|first=Ryan|last=Gaydos|date=2020-01-26|website=Fox News|accessdate=2020-01-26|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231546/https://www.foxnews.com/sports/california-helicopter-crash-calabasas-brush-fire-fatalities-reported|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/26/helicopter-crash-california-kills-5/4581709002/ |title=Investigation underway to determine cause of helicopter Calabasas, California, crash that killed Kobe Bryant |last=Bacon |first=John |date=2020-01-26 |website=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |access-date=2020-01-26 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231540/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2020/01/26/helicopter-crash-california-kills-5/4581709002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC51256756">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-51256756|title=Kobe Bryant: Basketball legend dies in helicopter crash|publisher=BBC News Online|accessdate=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126231904/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-51256756|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月28日，透過指紋方式確認科比的身份。隔天{{tsl|en|Los Angeles County Department of Medical Examiner-Coroner||洛杉磯縣驗屍部門}}表示，機上所有人員的死亡原因皆為{{tsl|en|blunt force trauma||鈍器受傷致死}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Coroner officials confirm IDs of five more people killed in crash of Kobe Bryant’s helicopter |url=https://www.dailynews.com/coroner-officials-confirm-ids-of-five-more-people-killed-in-crash-of-kobe-bryants-helicopter |website=DailyNews.com|date=2020-01-30}}</ref>。

2月7日，科比和二女兒吉安娜葬於[[新港滩|新港滩]]附近的{{tsl|en|Corona del Mar, Newport Beach||科羅納狄馬}}太平洋景觀墓園（Pacific View Memorial Park）<ref name="Boren">{{cite news |last1=Boren |first1=Cindy |title=Kobe Bryant and his daughter Gianna were buried near their home in a private service last week |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/02/12/kobe-bryant-burial-service/ |accessdate=2020-02-13 |work=The Washington Post |publisher=WP Company LLC |date=2020-02-12 |location=[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]] |archive-date=2020-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618033112/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/02/12/kobe-bryant-burial-service/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黃靖貽(譯) |author2=劉文瑜(核稿) |title=Kobe父女長眠加州私人墓園 追思日期別具意義 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202002130040.aspx |accessdate=2020-03-01 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-02-13 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111040340/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202002130040.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月24日，科比的公開追思會在[[洛杉磯市中心|洛杉磯市中心]]的[[斯台普斯中心|斯台普斯中心]]舉行<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/story/2020-02-07/vanessa-bryant-announces-a-celebration-of-life-for-kobe-and-gian|title=Vanessa Bryant announces 'A Celebration of Life' for Kobe and Gianna|first=Broderick|last=Turner|date=2020-02-07|accessdate=2020-02-09|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209004905/https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/story/2020-02-07/vanessa-bryant-announces-a-celebration-of-life-for-kobe-and-gian|archive-date=2020-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/02/07/kobe-bryant-memorial-service-staples-center/|title=Kobe Bryant public memorial service set for Feb. 24 at Staples Center|first=Desmond|last=Bieler|date=2020-02-07|accessdate=2020-02-09|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208151657/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2020/02/07/kobe-bryant-memorial-service-staples-center/|archive-date=2020-02-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/06/us/kobe-bryant-memorial-service/index.html|title=Kobe Bryant memorial service will be held February 24 at Staples Center|first1=Steve|last=Almasy|first2=Chloe|last2=Melas|date=2020-02-07|accessdate=2020-02-09|publisher=[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208125720/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/06/us/kobe-bryant-memorial-service/index.html|archive-date=2020-02-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

